title: Group Therapy: He's Flirting With Me And Has Known Me Since I Was 8
description: Alexia called the show today to talk about how she's getting inappropriate DM's from her friends dad who's married. He's known her since she was 8 and is unsure what to do. Should she tell her friend? confront him? Alexa is 22 years old and he's 55.
